=== test.175: msleep(100) after complete BAR2 firmware write — stage=0 ===
Date: Mon Apr 20 18:12:34 BST 2026

Stage 0: skip_arm=1 — download_fw_nvram: enter_download_state (read-only) + BAR2 ioread32 probe + 442KB iowrite32 fw; sleeps 100 ms after fw write complete, then releases fw/NVRAM and returns -ENODEV.
(test.175: test.174 proved immediate return after the complete fw write survives. This run adds msleep(100) after fw write complete, still with no post-write ARM probe, resetintr read, NVRAM write, or readback. Expected: survival implicates mdelay/busy-wait dwell; freeze implicates elapsed post-write time in the callback.)

=== Pre-test BAR0 MMIO guard ===
BAR0 MMIO UR/I/O error (6ms) — device alive; SBR in probe should fix. Proceeding.

